snippet.textDisplay:
Bro you need to go into community work. I sort of get it, making other people happy has often been my life line. Like being able to work with people whose lives are in tatters, and see smiles appear on their faces -there are fewer things better. Maybe you would rather stay a content creator, and you absolutely can - but you're obviously a people person. I've watched you since I was a kid, and to see how you are doing atm is devastating. I know coming out of depression is probably the hardest thing to do, but you must believe me when I say there is light at the end of every tunnel. The nature of this 'light' may not yet be clear to you, and it may take some adjusting, but it does exist. The hardest thing is knowing deep down that in your life, something needs to change. I'm not sure what it is, but in my experience, working towards finding it will set everything right,


You have an army of fans who love everything you are and do, me included. Honestly, I hope you find peace in your heart soon, you don't deserve any of this bs.I back you in mate, stay strong <3
